y in\nabsolute shear DOmega with temperature is consistent with the temperature\nscaling law found in Doppler Imaging measurements.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Sep 2005 17:05:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 30 Sep 2005 19:25:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-30"}
